    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "A key to the genera of Issini (Hemiptera: Fulgoromorpha: Issidae) of China and neighbouring countries, with descriptions of a new genus and two new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269260>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269261>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269262>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269263>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269265> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269260>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. A. Celyphoma quadrupla Meng & Wang, 2012, holotype, ♂, habitus, dorsal view. B. Same, lateral view. — C. Pseudochoutagus curvativus Che, Zhang & Wang, 2011, holotype, ♂, habitus, dorsal view. — D. Macrodarumoides petalinus Che, Zhang & Wang, 2012, holotype, ♂, frons and clypeus. E. Same, dorsal view. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/269260/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269261>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Tegmen. A. Sarima sp. B. Sarimodes sp. C. Eusarima sp. — Hind wing. D. Macrodarumoides petalinus Che, Zhang & Wang, 2012, holotype. E. Gelastyrella litaoensis Yang, 1994. F. Dentatissus damnosus (Chou & Lu, 1985). Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/269261/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269262>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. — A. Eusudasina nantouense Yang, 1994, frons and clypeus. B. Same, lateral view. — C. Gelastyrella litaoensis Yang, 1994, frons and clypeus. — D. Eusarima sp., frons and clypeus. — E. Dentatissus damnosus (Chou & Lu, 1985), penis, left view. F. Same, male genitalia, lateral view. G. Same, penis, ventral view. — H. Kodaianella bicinctifrons Fennah, 1956, male genitalia, lateral view. I. As previous, penis, left view. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/269262/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269263>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Orbita parallelodroma Meng & Wang, gen. et sp. nov., holotype. A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. Habitus, lateral view. C. Frons and clypeus. D. Head and thorax, latero-ventral view. E. Tegmen. F. Hind wing. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/269263/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269265>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Neokodaiana minensis Meng & Qin, sp. nov., holotype. A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. Habitus, lateral view. C. Frons and clypeus. D. Head and thorax, latero-ventral view. E. Male anal tube and pygofer, lateral view. F. Capitulum of style, dorsal view. G. Gonapophyses IX and gonaspiculum bridge, right view. H. Male anal tube, dorsal view. I. Connective. J. Penis, lateral view. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/269265/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

